overview: GoEmerchant is a leading provider of affordable E-commerce solutions for small businesses. GoEmerchant provides all the tools you need to accept credit cards online, including Internet merchant account, shopping cart software, secure payment gateway, E-commerce hosting, website hosting, marketing tools, and domain name registration. Additional credit card processing solutions include Multi-MID capability, Payment Plug-in for use with QuickBooks; Virtual Terminal accounts for manually keyed or swiped transactions; Batch Upload Gateway for high volume, offline transactions; Credit Card POS machines and Wireless Terminals for Retail merchants; and mobile solutions for iPhone, blackberry, and most smartphones.
